----------------------------------------------------------------------
This is the implementation of Multi-level Coarse-Graining in LIGGGHTS. 
This repository contains an example folder which showcases the capabilities
of MCG.

References: 
[1] Tarun De, Jayanta Chakraborty, Jitendra Kumar, Anurag Tripathi, Maitraye Sen, William Ketterhagen,
A particle location based multi-level coarse-graining technique for Discrete Element Method (DEM) simulation,
Powder Technology, Volume 398, 2022, 117058, https://doi.org/10.1016/j.powtec.2021.117058.

[2] Lokeshwar Mahto, Tarun De, Jayanta Chakraborty, Jitendra Kumar, Anurag Tripathi, Maitraye Sen, William Ketterhagen,
Accelerated DEM simulation of the hopper-screw feeder and tablet-press feeder using the multi-level coarse-graining technique,
Powder Technology, Volume 436, 2024, 119466, https://doi.org/10.1016/j.powtec.2024.119466.

